{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"You will understand nothing with my type of English."},{"time":5000,"text":"It's good for you because you can have a break after all these fantastic people."},{"time":14000,"text":"I must tell you I am like that, not very comfortable,"},{"time":19000,"text":"because usually, in life, I think my job is absolutely useless."},{"time":25000,"text":"I mean, I feel useless."},{"time":29000,"text":"Now after Carolyn, and all the other guys, I feel like shit."},{"time":37000,"text":"And definitively, I don't know why I am here,"},{"time":44000,"text":"but -- you know the nightmare you can have, like you are an impostor,"},{"time":48000,"text":"you arrive at the opera, and they push you, \"You must sing!\""},{"time":52000,"text":"I don't know. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"So, so, because I have nothing to show, nothing to say,"},{"time":64000,"text":"we shall try to speak about something else."},{"time":68000,"text":"We can start, if you want, by understanding --"},{"time":71000,"text":"it's just to start, it's not interesting, but -- how I work."},{"time":76000,"text":"When somebody comes to me and ask for what I am known,"},{"time":83000,"text":"I mean, yes, lemon squeezer, toilet brush, toothpick, beautiful toilet seats,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and why not -- a toothbrush?"},{"time":94000,"text":"I don't try to design the toothbrush."},{"time":99000,"text":"I don't try to say, \"Oh, that will be a beautiful object,\" or something like that."},{"time":102000,"text":"That doesn't interest me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"Because there is different types of design."},{"time":106000,"text":"The one, we can call it the cynical design,"},{"time":111000,"text":"that means the design invented by Raymond Loewy in the '50s,"},{"time":114000,"text":"who said, what is ugly is a bad sale, la laideur se vend mal, which is terrible."},{"time":121000,"text":"It means the design must be just the weapon for marketing,"},{"time":126000,"text":"for producer to make product more sexy, like that,"},{"time":130000,"text":"they sell more: it's shit, it's obsolete, it's ridiculous."},{"time":134000,"text":"I call that the cynical design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"After, there is the narcissistic design:"},{"time":143000,"text":"it's a fantastic designer who designs only for other fantastic designers. (Laughter)"},{"time":150000,"text":"After, there is people like me, who try to deserve to exist,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and who are so ashamed to make this useless job, who try to do it in another way,"},{"time":164000,"text":"and they try, I try, to not make the object for the object but for the result,"},{"time":171000,"text":"for the profit for the human being, the person who will use it."},{"time":176000,"text":"If we take the toothbrush -- I don't think about the toothbrush."},{"time":181000,"text":"I think, \"What will be the effect of the brush in the mouth?\""},{"time":186000,"text":"And to understand what will be the effect of the toothbrush in the mouth,"},{"time":191000,"text":"I must imagine: Who owns this mouth?"},{"time":195000,"text":"What is the life of the owner of this mouth? In what society [does] this guy live?"},{"time":201000,"text":"What civilization creates this society?"},{"time":206000,"text":"What animal species creates this civilization?"},{"time":210000,"text":"When I arrive -- and I take one minute, I am not so intelligent --"},{"time":215000,"text":"when I arrive at the level of animal species, that becomes real interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Me, I have strictly no power to change anything."},{"time":225000,"text":"But when I come back, I can understand why I shall not do it,"},{"time":230000,"text":"because today to not do it, it's more positive than do it, or how I shall do it."},{"time":238000,"text":"But to come back, where I am at the animal species, there is things to see."},{"time":245000,"text":"There is things to see, there is the big challenge."},{"time":248000,"text":"The big challenge in front of us."},{"time":251000,"text":"Because there is not a human production"},{"time":255000,"text":"which exists outside of what I call \"the big image.\""},{"time":260000,"text":"The big image is our story, our poetry, our romanticism."},{"time":265000,"text":"Our poetry is our mutation, our life."},{"time":270000,"text":"We must remember, and we can see that in any book of my son of 10 years old,"},{"time":275000,"text":"that life appears four billion years ago, around -- four billion point two?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283000,"text":"Voice offstage: Four point five."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"Yes, point five, OK, OK, OK! (Laughter) I'm a designer,"},{"time":289000,"text":"that's all, of Christmas gifts."},{"time":292000,"text":"And before, there was this soup, called \"soupe primordiale,\""},{"time":297000,"text":"this first soup -- bloop bloop bloop --"},{"time":301000,"text":"sort of dirty mud, no life, nothing."},{"time":304000,"text":"So then -- pshoo-shoo -- lightning -- pshoo -- arrive --"},{"time":308000,"text":"pshoo-shoo -- makes life -- bloop bloop -- and that dies."},{"time":311000,"text":"Some million years after -- pshoo-shoo, bloop-bloop -- ah, wake up!"},{"time":316000,"text":"At the end, finally, that succeeds, and life appears."},{"time":322000,"text":"We was so, so stupid. The most stupid bacteria."},{"time":329000,"text":"Even, I think, we copy our way to reproduce, you know what I mean,"},{"time":334000,"text":"and something of -- oh no, forget it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"After, we become a fish; after, we become a frog;"},{"time":343000,"text":"after, we become a monkey; after, we become what we are today: a super-monkey,"},{"time":350000,"text":"and the fun is, the super-monkey we are today, is at half of the story."},{"time":357000,"text":"Can you imagine? From that stupid bacteria to us,"},{"time":361000,"text":"with a microphone, with a computer, with an iPod: four billion years."},{"time":367000,"text":"And we know, and especially Carolyn knows, that when the sun will implode,"},{"time":375000,"text":"the earth will burn, explode, I don't know what,"},{"time":379000,"text":"and this is scheduled for four, four billion years?"},{"time":383000,"text":"Yes, she said, something like that. OK, that means we are at half of the story."},{"time":389000,"text":"Fantastic! It's a beauty!"},{"time":392000,"text":"Can you imagine? It's very symbolic."},{"time":394000,"text":"Because the bacteria we was had no idea of what we are today."},{"time":399000,"text":"And today, we have no idea of what we shall be in four billion years."},{"time":405000,"text":"And this territory is fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408000,"text":"That is our poetry. That is our beautiful story."},{"time":413000,"text":"It's our romanticism. Mu-ta-tion. We are mutants."},{"time":418000,"text":"And if we don't deeply understand, if we don't integrate that we are mutants,"},{"time":425000,"text":"we completely miss the story."},{"time":428000,"text":"Because every generation thinks we are the final one."},{"time":432000,"text":"We have a way to look at Earth like that, you know,"},{"time":435000,"text":"\"I am the man. The final man."},{"time":439000,"text":"You know, we mutate during four billion years before, but now, because it's me, we stop. Fin. (Laughter)"},{"time":445000,"text":"For the end, for the eternity, it is one with a red jacket.\""},{"time":451000,"text":"Something like that. I am not sure of that. (Laughter)"},{"time":456000,"text":"Because that is our intelligence of mutation and things like that."},{"time":462000,"text":"There is so many things to do; it's so fresh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466000,"text":"And here is something: nobody is obliged to be a genius,"},{"time":474000,"text":"but everybody is obliged to participate."},{"time":477000,"text":"And to participate, for a mutant, there is a minimum of exercise, a minimum of sport."},{"time":484000,"text":"We can say that."},{"time":486000,"text":"The first, if you want -- there is so many --"},{"time":488000,"text":"but one which is very easy to do, is the duty of vision."},{"time":494000,"text":"I can explain you. I shall try."},{"time":497000,"text":"If you walk like that, it's OK, it's OK, you can walk,"},{"time":506000,"text":"but perhaps, because you walk with the eyes like that, you will not see, oh, there is a hole."},{"time":512000,"text":"And you will fall, and you will die. Dangerous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"That's why, perhaps, you will try to have this angle of vision."},{"time":521000,"text":"OK, I can see, if I found something, up, up, and they continue, up up up."},{"time":528000,"text":"I raise the angle of vision, but it's still very -- selfish, selfish, egoiste -- yes, selfish."},{"time":537000,"text":"You, you survive. It's OK."},{"time":540000,"text":"If you raise the level of your eyes a little more you go,"},{"time":546000,"text":"\"I see you, oh my God you are here, how are you, I can help you,"},{"time":550000,"text":"I can design for you a new toothbrush, new toilet brush,\" something like that."},{"time":555000,"text":"I live in society; I live in community."},{"time":559000,"text":"It's OK. You start to be in the territory of intelligence, we can say."},{"time":567000,"text":"From this level, the more you can raise this angle of view,"},{"time":574000,"text":"the more you will be important for the society."},{"time":578000,"text":"The more you will rise, the more you will be important for the civilization."},{"time":583000,"text":"The more you will rise, to see far and high, like that,"},{"time":589000,"text":"the more you will be important for the story of our mutation."},{"time":593000,"text":"That means intelligent people are in this angle. That is intelligence."},{"time":600000,"text":"From this to here, that, it's genius."},{"time":604000,"text":"Ptolemy, Eratosthenes, Einstein, things like that."},{"time":608000,"text":"Nobody's obliged to be a genius."},{"time":610000,"text":"It's better, but nobody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"Take care, in this training, to be a good mutant."},{"time":619000,"text":"There is some danger, there is some trap. One trap: the vertical."},{"time":623000,"text":"Because at the vertical of us, if you look like that,"},{"time":626000,"text":"\"Ah! my God, there is God. Ah! God!\""},{"time":629000,"text":"God is a trap. God is the answer when we don't know the answer."},{"time":636000,"text":"That means, when your brain is not enough big, when you don't understand,"},{"time":644000,"text":"you go, \"Ah, it's God, it's God.\" That's ridiculous."},{"time":647000,"text":"That's why -- jump, like that? No, don't jump."},{"time":651000,"text":"Come back. Because, after, there is another trap."},{"time":654000,"text":"If you look like that, you look to the past,"},{"time":657000,"text":"or you look inside if you are very flexible, inside yourself."},{"time":661000,"text":"It's called schizophrenia, and you are dead also."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664000,"text":"That's why every morning, now, because you are a good mutant,"},{"time":669000,"text":"you will raise your angle of view."},{"time":673000,"text":"Out, more of the horizontal. You are an intelligence."},{"time":677000,"text":"Never forget -- like that, like that."},{"time":680000,"text":"It's very, very, very important."},{"time":683000,"text":"What, what else we can say about that? Why do that?"},{"time":692000,"text":"It's because we -- if we look from far, we see our line of evolution."},{"time":703000,"text":"This line of evolution is clearly positive."},{"time":708000,"text":"From far, this line looks very smooth, like that."},{"time":712000,"text":"But if you take a lens, like that, this line is ack, ack, ack, ack, ack. Like that."},{"time":719000,"text":"It's made of light and shadow."},{"time":724000,"text":"We can say light is civilization, shadow is barbaria."},{"time":728000,"text":"And it's very important to know where we are."},{"time":731000,"text":"Because some cycle, there is a spot in the cycle,"},{"time":737000,"text":"and you have not the same duty in the different parts of the cycle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"That means, we can imagine -- I don't say it was fantastic,"},{"time":749000,"text":"but in the '80s, there was not too much war, like that, it was --"},{"time":756000,"text":"we can imagine that the civilization can become civilized."},{"time":763000,"text":"In this case, people like me are acceptable."},{"time":767000,"text":"We can say, \"It's luxurious time.\""},{"time":770000,"text":"We have time to think, we have time to I don't know what,"},{"time":774000,"text":"speak about art and things like that."},{"time":776000,"text":"It's OK. We are in the light."},{"time":779000,"text":"But sometimes, like today, we fall, we fall so fast, so fast to shadow, we fall so fast to barbaria."},{"time":790000,"text":"With many, many, many, many face of barbaria."},{"time":795000,"text":"Because it's not, the barbaria we have today, it's perhaps not the barbaria we think."},{"time":802000,"text":"There is different type of barbaria."},{"time":804000,"text":"That's why we must adapt."},{"time":807000,"text":"That means, when barbaria is back, forget the beautiful chairs, forget the beautiful hotel,"},{"time":817000,"text":"forget design, even -- I'm sorry to say -- forget art."},{"time":820000,"text":"Forget all that. There is priority; there is urgency."},{"time":824000,"text":"You must go back to politics, you must go back to radicalization,"},{"time":828000,"text":"I'm sorry if that's not very English."},{"time":831000,"text":"You must go back to fight, to battle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833000,"text":"That's why today I'm so ashamed to make this job."},{"time":837000,"text":"That's why I am here, to try to do it the best possible."},{"time":842000,"text":"But I know that even I do it the best possible"},{"time":846000,"text":"-- that's why I'm the best -- it's nothing."},{"time":848000,"text":"Because it's not the right time."},{"time":850000,"text":"That's why I say that. I say that, because, I repeat, nothing exist if it's not in the good rhythym,"},{"time":861000,"text":"the rhythym of our beautiful dream, of this civilization."},{"time":866000,"text":"And because we must all work to finish this story."},{"time":872000,"text":"Because the scenario of this civilization"},{"time":876000,"text":"-- about love, progress, and things like that -- it's OK,"},{"time":880000,"text":"but there is so many different, other scenarios of other civilizations."},{"time":886000,"text":"This scenario, of this civilization, was about becoming powerful, intelligent,"},{"time":895000,"text":"like this idea we have invented, this concept of God."},{"time":899000,"text":"We are God now. We are. It's almost done."},{"time":903000,"text":"We have just to finish the story."},{"time":905000,"text":"That is very, very important."},{"time":907000,"text":"And when you don't understand really what's happened,"},{"time":911000,"text":"you cannot go and fight and work and build and things like that."},{"time":917000,"text":"You go to the future back, back, back, back, like that."},{"time":922000,"text":"And you can fall, and it's very dangerous."},{"time":924000,"text":"No, you must really understand that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928000,"text":"Because we have almost finished, I'll repeat this story."},{"time":932000,"text":"And the beauty of this, in perhaps 50 years, 60 years, we can finish completely this civilization,"},{"time":941000,"text":"and offer to our children the possibility to invent a new story,"},{"time":948000,"text":"a new poetry, a new romanticism."},{"time":950000,"text":"With billions of people who have been born, worked, lived and died before us,"},{"time":958000,"text":"these people who have worked so much,"},{"time":960000,"text":"we have now bring beautiful things, beautiful gifts, we know so many things."},{"time":967000,"text":"We can say to our children, OK, done, that was our story. That passed."},{"time":974000,"text":"Now you have a duty: invent a new story. Invent a new poetry."},{"time":980000,"text":"The only rule is, we have not to have any idea about the next story."},{"time":987000,"text":"We give you white pages. Invent."},{"time":992000,"text":"We give you the best tools, the best tools, and now, do it."},{"time":1000000,"text":"That's why I continue to work, even if it's for toilet brush."}]}]}